    • Field Detail

      • ACTION_NEW_MESSAGE

        public static final java.lang.String ACTION_NEW_MESSAGE
        Broadcast action: a new multimedia message has been received.

        Intent includes the following extras:

        • EXTRA_CONTACT containing the MSISDN of the contact sending the message.
        • EXTRA_DISPLAY_NAME containing the display name of the contact sending the message (extracted from the SIP address).
        • EXTRA_CONTENT containing the multimedia message content.
        • The service ID is read from the method Intent.getType() which returns the MIME type included in the intent and corresponding to the invoked service.
